#. type: Plain text
#: rw-FAQ.texi:550
msgid "We have had several reports of this, although they do work for us on @emph{all} of our machines.  There are two known possible causes."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: rw-FAQ.texi:552
msgid "(a) A proxy needs to be set up: see @code{?download.file}."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: rw-FAQ.texi:556
msgid "(b) Firewall settings are blocking the R executables from contacting the Internet (but this should result in informative error messages from the firewall program)."
