msgid "R commands can be interrupted by @key{Esc} in @command{Rgui.exe} and @key{Ctrl-break} or @key{Ctrl-C} in @command{Rterm.exe}: @key{Ctrl-C} is used for copying in @command{Rgui.exe}."
